 "notes": "#539 kills Sparkles-as-AI-marker everywhere (DESIGN.md 2026-07-17 freeze replaces with Astra orbital glyph + 'AI'/'IA' badge deleted). Web Loader2 has 15 usage counts (mobile Loader2 is 0 because mobile uses ActivityIndicator from React Native instead). ListChecks + ListTodo both resolve to IconListCheck in Tabler. CheckCircle + CheckCircle2 both use IconCircleCheck (CheckCircle2 is a Lucide variant). FastForward → IconPlayerSkipForward (Tabler's skip-forward variant). Settings2 → IconSliders (Tabler equivalent for secondary settings icon). HelpCircle → IconCircleQuestion (Lucide's help icon). All 86 distinct icons plus Shuffle (custom Orbit icon). Zero icon breakage risk: all Lucide names are 1:1 renames to Icon-prefixed Tabler names except the 5 marked uncertain (which have clear Tabler equivalents but need human verification on visual parity).\""
}